{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":764,"text":"G'day, my name's Kevin."},{"time":2923,"text":"I'm from Australia. I'm here to help."},{"time":5616,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":8147,"text":"Tonight, I want to talk about\na tale of two cities."},{"time":12814,"text":"One of those cities is called Washington,\nand the other is called Beijing."},{"time":18248,"text":"Because how these two capitals\nshape their future"},{"time":24284,"text":"and the future of the United States\nand the future of China"},{"time":27489,"text":"doesn't just affect those two countries,"},{"time":29578,"text":"it affects all of us"},{"time":31900,"text":"in ways, perhaps, we've never thought of:"},{"time":34780,"text":"the air we breathe, the water we drink,"},{"time":39145,"text":"the fish we eat,\nthe quality of our oceans,"},{"time":42279,"text":"the languages we speak in the future,"},{"time":45948,"text":"the jobs we have,\nthe political systems we choose,"},{"time":48873,"text":"and, of course, the great questions\nof war and peace."}]},{"cues":[{"time":54024,"text":"You see that bloke? He's French."},{"time":57279,"text":"His name is Napoleon."},{"time":59109,"text":"A couple of hundred years ago,"},{"time":60645,"text":"he made this extraordinary projection:"},{"time":63083,"text":"\"China is a sleeping lion,\nand when she awakes,"},{"time":65707,"text":"the world will shake.\""},{"time":67913,"text":"Napoleon got a few things wrong;"},{"time":70096,"text":"he got this one absolutely right."},{"time":72789,"text":"Because China is today\nnot just woken up,"},{"time":77061,"text":"China has stood up\nand China is on the march,"},{"time":80521,"text":"and the question for us all"},{"time":82541,"text":"is where will China go"},{"time":84515,"text":"and how do we engage\nthis giant of the 21st century?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":91003,"text":"You start looking at the numbers,\nthey start to confront you in a big way."},{"time":95381,"text":"It's projected that China will become,"},{"time":98492,"text":"by whichever measure --\nPPP, market exchange rates --"},{"time":101906,"text":"the largest economy in the world"},{"time":103833,"text":"over the course of the decade ahead."},{"time":106039,"text":"They're already\nthe largest trading nation,"},{"time":108190,"text":"already the largest exporting nation,"},{"time":110341,"text":"already the largest manufacturing nation,"},{"time":112494,"text":"and they're also the biggest\nemitters of carbon in the world."},{"time":116859,"text":"America comes second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":119343,"text":"So if China does become\nthe world's largest economy,"},{"time":124869,"text":"think about this:"},{"time":126495,"text":"It'll be the first time"},{"time":129513,"text":"since this guy was on\nthe throne of England --"},{"time":134180,"text":"George III, not a good friend\nof Napoleon's --"},{"time":137663,"text":"that in the world we will have\nas the largest economy"},{"time":143102,"text":"a non-English speaking country,"},{"time":145488,"text":"a non-Western country,"},{"time":147694,"text":"a non-liberal democratic country."},{"time":150021,"text":"And if you don't think\nthat's going to affect"},{"time":152314,"text":"the way in which the world\nhappens in the future,"},{"time":155077,"text":"then personally, I think\nyou've been smoking something,"},{"time":158305,"text":"and it doesn't mean you're from Colorado."}]},{"cues":[{"time":162925,"text":"So in short, the question\nwe have tonight is,"},{"time":165711,"text":"how do we understand this mega-change,"},{"time":168707,"text":"which I believe to be the biggest change\nfor the first half of the 21st century?"},{"time":173490,"text":"It'll affect so many things."},{"time":176415,"text":"It will go to the absolute core."},{"time":178157,"text":"It's happening quietly.\nIt's happening persistently."},{"time":180804,"text":"It's happening in some senses\nunder the radar,"},{"time":183358,"text":"as we are all preoccupied with"},{"time":185103,"text":"what's going in Ukraine,\nwhat's going on in the Middle East,"},{"time":187932,"text":"what's going on with ISIS,\nwhat's going on with ISIL,"},{"time":190440,"text":"what's happening with\nthe future of our economies."},{"time":193412,"text":"This is a slow and quiet revolution."},{"time":197684,"text":"And with a mega-change\ncomes also a mega-challenge,"},{"time":203373,"text":"and the mega-challenge is this:"},{"time":205044,"text":"Can these two great countries,"},{"time":207297,"text":"China and the United States --"},{"time":209897,"text":"China,"},{"time":215725,"text":"the Middle Kingdom,"},{"time":217374,"text":"and the United States,"},{"time":222343,"text":"Měiguó --"},{"time":225547,"text":"which in Chinese, by the way,\nmeans \"the beautiful country.\""},{"time":228890,"text":"Think about that -- that's the name\nthat China has given this country"},{"time":232514,"text":"for more than a hundred years."},{"time":234254,"text":"Whether these two great civilizations,\nthese two great countries,"},{"time":237853,"text":"can in fact carve out a common future"},{"time":242056,"text":"for themselves and for the world?"},{"time":244633,"text":"In short, can we carve out a future"},{"time":247605,"text":"which is peaceful and mutually prosperous,"},{"time":251044,"text":"or are we looking at a great challenge"},{"time":252948,"text":"of war or peace?"},{"time":255316,"text":"And I have 15 minutes\nto work through war or peace,"},{"time":257940,"text":"which is a little less time"},{"time":261493,"text":"than they gave this guy to write a book\ncalled \"War and Peace.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":266486,"text":"People ask me, why is it that a kid\ngrowing up in rural Australia"},{"time":270664,"text":"got interested in learning Chinese?"},{"time":272452,"text":"Well, there are two reasons for that."},{"time":274310,"text":"Here's the first of them."},{"time":275936,"text":"That's Betsy the cow."},{"time":277955,"text":"Now, Betsy the cow was one\nof a herd of dairy cattle"},{"time":281880,"text":"that I grew up with on a farm\nin rural Australia."},{"time":285050,"text":"See those hands there?\nThese are not built for farming."},{"time":288543,"text":"So very early on, I discovered\nthat in fact, working in a farm"},{"time":292281,"text":"was not designed for me,\nand China was a very safe remove"},{"time":295927,"text":"from any career in Australian farm life."}]},{"cues":[{"time":298318,"text":"Here's the second reason."},{"time":300013,"text":"That's my mom."},{"time":300918,"text":"Anyone here ever listen\nto what their mom told them to do?"},{"time":303682,"text":"Everyone ever do what\ntheir mom told them to do?"},{"time":306352,"text":"I rarely did,"},{"time":308256,"text":"but what my mom said to me was,"},{"time":310151,"text":"one day, she handed me a newspaper,"},{"time":313030,"text":"a headline which said,\nhere we have a huge change."},{"time":318881,"text":"And that change is China\nentering the United Nations."},{"time":324274,"text":"1971, I had just turned 14 years of age,"},{"time":327193,"text":"and she handed me this headline."},{"time":329470,"text":"And she said, \"Understand this, \nlearn this,"},{"time":331657,"text":"because it's going to affect your future.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":334563,"text":"So being a very good student of history,"},{"time":338361,"text":"I decided that the best thing\nfor me to do was, in fact,"},{"time":341032,"text":"to go off and learn Chinese."},{"time":343284,"text":"The great thing about learning Chinese"},{"time":345397,"text":"is that your Chinese teacher\ngives you a new name."},{"time":348508,"text":"And so they gave me this name:"},{"time":351434,"text":"Kè, which means to overcome or to conquer,"},{"time":356565,"text":"and Wén, and that's the character\nfor literature or the arts."},{"time":361163,"text":"Kè Wén, Conqueror of the Classics."},{"time":365528,"text":"Any of you guys called \"Kevin\"?"},{"time":368175,"text":"It's a major lift from being called Kevin\nto be called Conqueror of the Classics."},{"time":372256,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":373907,"text":"I've been called Kevin all my life."},{"time":375649,"text":"Have you been called Kevin all your life?"},{"time":377637,"text":"Would you prefer to be called\nConqueror of the Classics?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":380838,"text":"And so I went off after that\nand joined the Australian Foreign Service,"},{"time":384396,"text":"but here is where pride -- before pride,\nthere always comes a fall."},{"time":391022,"text":"So there I am in the embassy in Beijing,"},{"time":393530,"text":"off to the Great Hall of the People"},{"time":395736,"text":"with our ambassador, who had asked me\nto interpret for his first meeting"},{"time":399130,"text":"in the Great Hall of the People."},{"time":401146,"text":"And so there was I."},{"time":402634,"text":"If you've been to a Chinese meeting,\nit's a giant horseshoe."},{"time":405475,"text":"At the head of the horsehoe\nare the really serious pooh-bahs,"},{"time":408353,"text":"and down the end of the horseshoe\nare the not-so-serious pooh-bahs,"},{"time":411515,"text":"the junior woodchucks like me."},{"time":413940,"text":"And so the ambassador\nbegan with this inelegant phrase."},{"time":416726,"text":"He said, \"China and Australia\nare currently enjoying a relationship"},{"time":421370,"text":"of unprecedented closeness.\""},{"time":424922,"text":"And I thought to myself,"},{"time":426408,"text":"\"That sounds clumsy. That sounds odd."},{"time":430170,"text":"I will improve it.\""},{"time":432468,"text":"Note to file: Never do that."},{"time":435202,"text":"It needed to be a little more elegant,\na little more classical,"},{"time":438191,"text":"so I rendered it as follows."},{"time":440490,"text":"[In Chinese]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445621,"text":"There was a big pause\non the other side of the room."},{"time":448848,"text":"You could see the giant pooh-bahs\nat the head of the horseshoe,"},{"time":452633,"text":"the blood visibly draining\nfrom their faces,"},{"time":455628,"text":"and the junior woodchucks\nat the other end of the horseshoe"},{"time":458577,"text":"engaged in peals of \nunrestrained laughter."},{"time":461364,"text":"Because when I rendered his sentence,"},{"time":463158,"text":"\"Australia and China are \nenjoying a relationship"},{"time":465473,"text":"of unprecedented closeness,\""},{"time":467558,"text":"in fact, what I said was that\nAustralia and China"},{"time":470024,"text":"were now experiencing fantastic orgasm."},{"time":473252,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":479428,"text":"That was the last time\nI was asked to interpret."},{"time":483050,"text":"But in that little story,\nthere's a wisdom, which is,"},{"time":485558,"text":"as soon as you think you know something\nabout this extraordinary civilization"},{"time":489412,"text":"of 5,000 years of continuing history,"},{"time":491618,"text":"there's always something new to learn."}]},{"cues":[{"time":495580,"text":"History is against us"},{"time":497678,"text":"when it comes to the U.S. and China"},{"time":499907,"text":"forging a common future together."},{"time":502206,"text":"This guy up here?"},{"time":503644,"text":"He's not Chinese and he's not American."},{"time":505573,"text":"He's Greek. His name's Thucydides."},{"time":507802,"text":"He wrote the history\nof the Peloponnesian Wars."},{"time":510286,"text":"And he made this extraordinary observation\n"},{"time":513064,"text":"about Athens and Sparta."},{"time":515412,"text":"\"It was the rise of Athens\nand the fear that this inspired in Sparta"},{"time":518622,"text":"that made war inevitable.\""},{"time":520154,"text":"And hence, a whole literature about\nsomething called the Thucydides Trap."}]},{"cues":[{"time":525471,"text":"This guy here? He's not American\nand he's not Greek. He's Chinese."},{"time":529303,"text":"His name is Sun Tzu.\nHe wrote \"The Art of War,\""},{"time":531674,"text":"and if you see his statement underneath,\nit's along these lines:"},{"time":535197,"text":"\"Attack him where he is unprepared,\nappear where you are not expected.\""},{"time":540424,"text":"Not looking good so far\nfor China and the United States."}]},{"cues":[{"time":544430,"text":"This guy is an American.\nHis name's Graham Allison."},{"time":547309,"text":"In fact, he's a teacher\nat the Kennedy School"},{"time":549909,"text":"over there in Boston."},{"time":551187,"text":"He's working on a single project\nat the moment, which is,"},{"time":554159,"text":"does the Thucydides Trap\nabout the inevitably of war"},{"time":557340,"text":"between rising powers\nand established great powers"},{"time":560428,"text":"apply to the future\nof China-U.S. relations?"},{"time":563400,"text":"It's a core question."},{"time":564819,"text":"And what Graham has done\nis explore 15 cases in history"},{"time":568860,"text":"since the 1500s"},{"time":571321,"text":"to establish what the precedents are."},{"time":573852,"text":"And in 11 out of 15 of them,"},{"time":575848,"text":"let me tell you,"},{"time":577915,"text":"they've ended in catastrophic war."}]},{"cues":[{"time":581050,"text":"You may say, \"But Kevin --"},{"time":584486,"text":"or Conqueror of the Classics --"},{"time":586785,"text":"that was the past."},{"time":588967,"text":"We live now in a world\nof interdependence and globalization."},{"time":592102,"text":"It could never happen again.\""},{"time":593565,"text":"Guess what?"},{"time":594911,"text":"The economic historians\ntell us that in fact,"},{"time":597581,"text":"the time which we reached\nthe greatest point"},{"time":599900,"text":"of economic integration and globalization"},{"time":602719,"text":"was in 1914,"},{"time":605290,"text":"just before that happened, World War I,"},{"time":609423,"text":"a sobering reflection from history."}]},{"cues":[{"time":612511,"text":"So if we are engaged\nin this great question"},{"time":615065,"text":"of how China thinks, feels,"},{"time":618270,"text":"and positions itself\ntowards the United States,"},{"time":622147,"text":"and the reverse,"},{"time":623633,"text":"how do we get to the baseline"},{"time":625514,"text":"of how these two countries\nand civilizations"},{"time":628904,"text":"can possibly work together?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":631830,"text":"Let me first go to, in fact,"},{"time":634128,"text":"China's views of the U.S.\nand the rest of the West."},{"time":636729,"text":"Number one: China feels\nas if it's been humiliated"},{"time":639604,"text":"at the hands of the West\nthrough a hundred years of history,"},{"time":642487,"text":"beginning with the Opium Wars."},{"time":644275,"text":"When after that, the Western powers\ncarved China up into little pieces,"},{"time":648083,"text":"so that by the time\nit got to the '20s and '30s,"},{"time":650614,"text":"signs like this one appeared\non the streets of Shanghai."},{"time":653291,"text":"[\"No dogs and Chinese allowed\"]"},{"time":654786,"text":"How would you feel if you were Chinese, \n"},{"time":656756,"text":"in your own country, \nif you saw that sign appear?"},{"time":659539,"text":"China also believes and feels"},{"time":663407,"text":"as if, in the events of 1919,\nat the Peace Conference in Paris,"},{"time":668028,"text":"when Germany's colonies were given back"},{"time":669924,"text":"to all sorts of countries\naround in the world,"},{"time":672068,"text":"what about German colonies in China?"},{"time":673926,"text":"They were, in fact, given to Japan."},{"time":676480,"text":"When Japan then invaded China in the 1930s"},{"time":680589,"text":"the world looked away and was indifferent\nto what would happen to China."},{"time":684257,"text":"And then, on top of that,\nthe Chinese to this day believe"},{"time":687114,"text":"that the United States and the West"},{"time":688801,"text":"do not accept the legitimacy\nof their political system"},{"time":691333,"text":"because it's so radically different\nfrom those of us who come"},{"time":694223,"text":"from liberal democracies,"},{"time":695513,"text":"and believe that the United States\nto this day is seeking"},{"time":698329,"text":"to undermine their political system."},{"time":700767,"text":"China also believes\nthat it is being contained"},{"time":703785,"text":"by U.S. allies and by those\nwith strategic partnerships with the U.S."},{"time":708638,"text":"right around its periphery."},{"time":711262,"text":"And beyond all that,\nthe Chinese have this feeling"},{"time":713746,"text":"in their heart of hearts\nand in their gut of guts"},{"time":716974,"text":"that those of us in the collective West"},{"time":721176,"text":"are just too damned arrogant."},{"time":724868,"text":"That is, we don't recognize\nthe problems in our own system,"},{"time":728815,"text":"in our politics and our economics,"},{"time":730673,"text":"and are very quick\nto point the finger elsewhere,"},{"time":733064,"text":"and believe that, in fact,\nwe in the collective West"},{"time":736826,"text":"are guilty of a great bunch of hypocrisy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":740634,"text":"Of course, in international relations,"},{"time":744047,"text":"it's not just the sound\nof one hand clapping."},{"time":748006,"text":"There's another country too,\nand that's called the U.S."},{"time":750688,"text":"So how does the U.S.\nrespond to all of the above?"},{"time":753242,"text":"The U.S. has a response to each of those."},{"time":755378,"text":"On the question of\nis the U.S. containing China,"},{"time":757881,"text":"they say, \"No, look at the history of\nthe Soviet Union. That was containment.\""},{"time":761559,"text":"Instead, what we have done\nin the U.S. and the West"},{"time":763969,"text":"is welcome China\ninto the global economy,"},{"time":765943,"text":"and on top of that, welcome them\ninto the World Trade Organization."},{"time":769379,"text":"The U.S. and the West say China cheats"},{"time":771252,"text":"on the question\nof intellectual property rights,"},{"time":773558,"text":"and through cyberattacks\non U.S. and global firms."},{"time":777877,"text":"Furthermore, the United States\nsays that the Chinese political system"},{"time":781453,"text":"is fundamentally wrong"},{"time":784332,"text":"because it's at such fundamental variance"},{"time":787629,"text":"to the human rights, democracy,\nand rule of law that we enjoy"},{"time":790880,"text":"in the U.S. and the collective West."},{"time":793504,"text":"And on top of all the above,\nwhat does the United States say?"},{"time":796661,"text":"That they fear that China will,\nwhen it has sufficient power,"},{"time":801769,"text":"establish a sphere of influence\nin Southeast Asia and wider East Asia,"},{"time":805786,"text":"boot the United States out,"},{"time":807690,"text":"and in time, when it's powerful enough,"},{"time":809710,"text":"unilaterally seek to change\nthe rules of the global order."}]},{"cues":[{"time":813719,"text":"So apart from all of that,\nit's just fine and dandy,"},{"time":816421,"text":"the U.S.-China relationship."},{"time":817815,"text":"No real problems there."},{"time":820020,"text":"The challenge, though,\nis given those deep-rooted feelings,"},{"time":824942,"text":"those deep-rooted emotions\nand thought patterns,"},{"time":827937,"text":"what the Chinese call \"Sīwéi,\"\nways of thinking,"},{"time":830747,"text":"how can we craft a basis\nfor a common future between these two?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":835205,"text":"I argue simply this:"},{"time":836836,"text":"We can do it on the basis on a framework"},{"time":838781,"text":"of constructive realism\nfor a common purpose."},{"time":843356,"text":"What do I mean by that?"},{"time":845329,"text":"Be realistic about the things\nthat we disagree on,"},{"time":847674,"text":"and a management approach\nthat doesn't enable"},{"time":849949,"text":"any one of those differences\nto break into war or conflict"},{"time":852805,"text":"until we've acquired\nthe diplomatic skills to solve them."},{"time":856358,"text":"Be constructive in areas of the\nbilateral, regional and global engagement"},{"time":860014,"text":"between the two,"},{"time":861386,"text":"which will make a difference\nfor all of humankind."},{"time":864113,"text":"Build a regional institution\ncapable of cooperation in Asia,"},{"time":868106,"text":"an Asia-Pacific community."},{"time":870034,"text":"And worldwide, act further,"},{"time":872448,"text":"like you've begun to do\nat the end of last year"},{"time":875072,"text":"by striking out against climate change"},{"time":877301,"text":"with hands joined together\nrather than fists apart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":881295,"text":"Of course, all that happens\nif you've got a common mechanism"},{"time":884197,"text":"and political will to achieve the above."},{"time":886310,"text":"These things are deliverable."},{"time":889004,"text":"But the question is,\nare they deliverable alone?"},{"time":893020,"text":"This is what our head\ntells us we need to do,"},{"time":895969,"text":"but what about our heart?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":897873,"text":"I have a little experience\nin the question back home"},{"time":900915,"text":"of how you try to bring\ntogether two peoples"},{"time":904235,"text":"who, frankly, haven't had\na whole lot in common in the past."},{"time":907857,"text":"And that's when I apologized\nto Australia's indigenous peoples."},{"time":911434,"text":"This was a day of reckoning\nin the Australian government,"},{"time":915219,"text":"the Australian parliament,\nand for the Australian people."},{"time":917911,"text":"After 200 years of unbridled abuse\ntowards the first Australians,"},{"time":922694,"text":"it was high time that we white folks\nsaid we were sorry."}]},{"cues":[{"time":927872,"text":"The important thing --"},{"time":929242,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":934288,"text":"The important thing that I remember\nis staring in the faces"},{"time":937210,"text":"of all those from Aboriginal Australia"},{"time":939691,"text":"as they came to listen to this apology."},{"time":942500,"text":"It was extraordinary to see, for example,"},{"time":946308,"text":"old women telling me the stories\nof when they were five years old"},{"time":950232,"text":"and literally ripped away\nfrom their parents,"},{"time":953228,"text":"like this lady here."},{"time":954829,"text":"It was extraordinary for me\nto then be able to embrace"},{"time":958962,"text":"and to kiss Aboriginal elders\nas they came into the parliament building,"},{"time":962910,"text":"and one woman said to me,"},{"time":964166,"text":"it's the first time a white fella\nhad ever kissed her in her life,"},{"time":967321,"text":"and she was over 70."},{"time":969272,"text":"That's a terrible story."}]},{"cues":[{"time":971779,"text":"And then I remember\nthis family saying to me,"},{"time":974241,"text":"\"You know, we drove all the way\nfrom the far North down to Canberra"},{"time":978304,"text":"to come to this thing,"},{"time":979674,"text":"drove our way through redneck country."},{"time":981857,"text":"On the way back, stopped at a cafe\nafter the apology for a milkshake.\""},{"time":988474,"text":"And they walked into this cafe\nquietly, tentatively, gingerly,"},{"time":994046,"text":"a little anxious."},{"time":995509,"text":"I think you know what I'm talking about."},{"time":998063,"text":"But the day after the apology,\nwhat happened?"},{"time":1001871,"text":"Everyone in that cafe,\nevery one of the white folks,"},{"time":1005981,"text":"stood up and applauded."},{"time":1008767,"text":"Something had happened in the hearts\nof these people in Australia."},{"time":1013903,"text":"The white folks, our Aboriginal\nbrothers and sisters,"},{"time":1016592,"text":"and we haven't solved\nall these problems together,"},{"time":1019820,"text":"but let me tell you,\nthere was a new beginning"},{"time":1023488,"text":"because we had gone not just to the head,"},{"time":1025904,"text":"we'd gone also to the heart."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1028562,"text":"So where does that conclude\nin terms of the great question"},{"time":1031433,"text":"that we've been asked\nto address this evening,"},{"time":1033620,"text":"which is the future\nof U.S.-China relations?"},{"time":1036584,"text":"The head says there's a way forward."},{"time":1038883,"text":"The head says there is a policy framework,\nthere's a common narrative,"},{"time":1042574,"text":"there's a mechanism\nthrough regular summitry"},{"time":1044501,"text":"to do these things\nand to make them better."},{"time":1046405,"text":"But the heart must also find a way\nto reimagine the possibilities"},{"time":1051978,"text":"of the America-China relationship,"},{"time":1053882,"text":"and the possibilities of China's\nfuture engagement in the world."},{"time":1057542,"text":"Sometimes, folks, we just need\nto take a leap of faith"},{"time":1063625,"text":"not quite knowing where we might land."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1067549,"text":"In China, they now talk about\nthe Chinese Dream."},{"time":1071822,"text":"In America, we're all familiar\nwith the term \"the American Dream.\""},{"time":1077348,"text":"I think it's time, across the world,"},{"time":1080482,"text":"that we're able to think also\nof something we might also call"},{"time":1085614,"text":"a dream for all humankind."},{"time":1091368,"text":"Because if we do that,"},{"time":1093327,"text":"we might just change the way"},{"time":1095977,"text":"that we think about each other."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1103923,"text":"[In Chinese]"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1107034,"text":"That's my challenge to America.\nThat's my challenge to China."},{"time":1110401,"text":"That's my challenge to all of us,"},{"time":1112885,"text":"but I think where there's a will\nand where there is imagination"},{"time":1116182,"text":"we can turn this into a future"},{"time":1118226,"text":"driven by peace and prosperity"},{"time":1120571,"text":"and not once again repeat"},{"time":1122591,"text":"the tragedies of war."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1124704,"text":"I thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1126562,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":1131997,"text":"Chris Anderson: Thanks so much for that.\nThanks so much for that."},{"time":1135176,"text":"It feels like you yourself\nhave a role to play in this bridging."},{"time":1139773,"text":"You, in a way, are uniquely placed\nto speak to both sides."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1144124,"text":"Kevin Rudd: Well, what we Australians\ndo best is organize the drinks,"},{"time":1147377,"text":"so you get them together in one room,\nand we suggest this and suggest that,"},{"time":1150904,"text":"then we go and get the drinks."},{"time":1152337,"text":"But no, look, for all of us\nwho are friends"},{"time":1154341,"text":"of these two great countries,\nAmerica and China,"},{"time":1156603,"text":"you can do something."},{"time":1157942,"text":"You can make a practical contribution,"},{"time":1160241,"text":"and for all you good folks here,"},{"time":1162122,"text":"next time you meet someone from China,"},{"time":1163747,"text":"sit down and have a conversation."},{"time":1165359,"text":"See what you can find out about\nwhere they come from and what they think,"},{"time":1168814,"text":"and my challenge for all\nthe Chinese folks"},{"time":1170852,"text":"who are going to watch\nthis TED Talk at some time"},{"time":1173181,"text":"is do the same."},{"time":1175542,"text":"Two of us seeking to change the world\ncan actually make a huge difference."},{"time":1179443,"text":"Those of us up the middle,\nwe can make a small contribution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1182345,"text":"CA: Kevin, all power to you,\nmy friend. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1184701,"text":"KR: Thank you. Thank you, folks."}]},{"cues":[{"time":1186827,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}